Hi <@U051LNXBB46>!

Is <https://developers.HubSpot.com/docs/reference/cms/hubl/functions#hubdb_table_column|this> what you are looking for?
You can do something like:
```{% set filters = hubdb_table_column({hubdbID}, "column_name").options %}
{% for filter in filters %}
  {{filter.name}}
{% endfor %} ```
Hope it helps!
